Converts a `&mut str` into a `Box<str>`

This conversion allocates on the heap
and performs a copy of `s`.

# Examples

```rust
let mut original = String::from("hello");
let original: &mut str = &mut original;
let boxed: Box<str> = Box::from(original);
println!("{boxed}");
```
